model

Class Identity

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Identity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Identity
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Identity class is essentially the tag associated to any Photo object. An Identity is used, in connection to a Key to search for Photo object that contains identical connections. A tag is identified by its name, type String, and each tag hold an ArrayList of Key objects associated to the tag.
    Author:
    Pedro Cruz
